Place the pot on the counter to the right of and behind the salt shaker.
Step right and walk to the sink.
Take the apple out of the sink.
Step left to where the pot now is.
Put the apple in the pot.
Go back to the sink.
Pick up the knife.
Walk back to the counter where the pot is and put the apple in the pot.
Cut the apple in the pot.

Turn left and carry the apple to the counter to your right.
